      "created": "2016-09-27T22:17:09.321+0000",
      "description": "As discussed in YARN-3981, we need the service discovery mechanism to map collectors with their actual \"ids\", which may or may not be a concrete application Id. This JIRA proposes to generalize the concept of collector id in collector service discovery mechanism. ",
      "priority": {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/priority/3",
