                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Li Lu",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Upload a patch to extend collector representations in RMs and NMs. After this change, collectors are not solely mapped to applications, but can have more general mappings identified by collector ids. Collector id is a string and can be generated by some utility methods for app-level collectors. \n\nThe current patch is based on the latest YARN-3359 patch, which is based on YARN-5638. Any comments are more than welcome. ",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gtcarrera9",
              "name": "gtcarrera9",
              "key": "gtcarrera9",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Li Lu",
