              "displayName": "Varun Saxena",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata"
            },
            "body": "Thanks [~gtCarrera9] for the patch. The patch does not apply cleanly for me on top of latest patches on YARN-3359 and YARN-5638. It will be easier to review if you can update all the patches.\n\nI had a scan through the patch as such though. Few comments thus far :\n* In GetTimelineCollectorContextRequestPBImpl, need to set type too in mergeLocalToBuilder\n* In CollectorData, should this be && ?\n{code}\n88\t  public boolean stamped() {\n89\t    return (getRMIdentifier() != UNSTAMPED_VERSION_NUMBER)\n90\t        || (getVersion() != UNSTAMPED_VERSION_NUMBER);\n91\t  }\n92\t\n{code}\n* In NodeHeartbeatRequestPBImpl, any need of setting RM ID and version ? IIUC, RM will report this in NM heartbeat response. How will NM be knowing about it ?\n* In NodeHeartbeatRequestPBImpl, rename addAppCollectorsMapToProto => addCollectorsMapToProto\n\n",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=varun_saxena",
